Invocation Name: my wedding ceremony
des:
It’s time to start practicing for your Big Day!

This skill will take you down the aisle and put you in front of your True Love.

Be sure to dress up! You can do your hair and you can practice walking in your shoes. And then do it over and over again.

Be sure to read your vows out loud and in front of the mirror. Practice reading them with a steady and slow pace until you feel confident and calm.

So, what are you waiting for?
